OL,3,CWigan man becomes 100th to be
OL,4,Csentenced over riots in Merseyside
OL,6,FA man has been jailed for his role in
OL,7,Friots in Southport last summer,
OL,8,Fbecoming the 100th person to be
OL,9,Fsentenced in connection with the
OL,10,Fviolent disorder in Merseyside.
OL,12,FPeter Fairhurst, 33, of Scot Lane, in
OL,13,FWigan, appeared at Liverpool Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Tuesday. He admitted the
OL,15,Foffence of violent disorder and was
OL,16,Fjailed for two years and two months.
