OL,4,Csentenced over riots in Merseyside
OL,6,FPolice say Fairhurst was at the
OL,7,Fforefront of violence in Southport on
OL,8,Fthe 30th July 2024, and could be seen
OL,9,Fon CCTV footage throwing bricks at
OL,10,Fofficers and police vehicles.
OL,12,FFairhurst's sentence pushes the
OL,13,Fcombined total of those jailed for the
OL,14,Fviolence in Southport and Liverpool to
OL,15,F200 years and six months in prison.
OL,17,FDetective Inspector Paula Jones said:
OL,18,F"The 100th person to be sentenced is a
OL,19,Fsignificant milestone to reach, but
OL,20,Fdoes not mark the end of the road for
OL,21,Four enquiries.
