OL,6,F"You will continue to see arrests,
OL,7,Fcharges and sentencings going through
OL,8,Fthe courts on a weekly basis. We make
OL,9,Fno apologies for this, and we know the
OL,10,Fvast majority of people in our
OL,11,Fcommunities support the robust action
OL,12,Fthat is being taken against these
OL,13,Fcriminals who are convicted, locally
OL,14,Fand nationally.
