OL,3,CWigan man becomes 100th to be
OL,4,Csentenced over riots in Merseyside
OL,6,F"The scenes in Southport, Walton and
OL,7,FLiverpool city centre were utterly
OL,8,Fdisgraceful, and every single person
OL,9,Finvolved brought shame upon
OL,10,Fthemselves. More importantly, their
OL,11,Factions caused further trauma and
OL,12,Fsuffering to communities that were in
OL,13,Fshock.
OL,15,F"We will not rest until we've put
OL,16,Feveryone we possibly can before the
OL,17,Fcourts. To that end, I'd continue to
OL,18,Fencourage anyone with information to
OL,19,Fget in touch anonymously via
OL,20,FCrimestoppers on 0800 555 111."
